headline: CrowdStrike Stock’s 54.8% Rally in 2025: Are New Contracts Driving a Fair Price?
summary: Wondering if CrowdStrike Holdings stock is a hidden bargain or priced for perfection? Let’s dig into what the numbers and recent momentum can tell us. While the stock is up a striking 54.8% year-to-date and 59.6% over the past year, it also saw a minor dip of 0.4% in the last week.
